history.content: This is due to a bug in student systems but a work-around has been implemented and I believe the labs for 61ABC will be visible by no later than first thing tomorrow morning.
The sections are plentiful and as a result don't really change much from semester to semester - just check out the current website and scroll down.

Is there a way I can view the available lab sections for 61B? I've run Chrome and Safari on 61B's classes.berkeley.edu page, but I can only see the available discussion sections. Since discussion and lab are both paired, I would like know what the corresponding lab section is for discussion so I can plan my schedule.
